Package: AdaStableNet
Title: Adaptive Eigenvalue-Based Estimation of Linear ODE Systems
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Ricardo J.", "Lopez Candelaria", 
                  email = "rlopez.research@gmail.com", 
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Implements adaptive estimation of dynamic system matrices from multivariate time series 
    using a two-stage approach and penalized eigenvalue stability. Includes smoothing, basis 
    construction, ridge inversion, and penalized fitting with optional Torch support.
